{
  "stem": "58.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The-- we could hear, the Russians had they called [? katyushas. ?] Like a artillery that you-- like missiles.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You put them in tubes, like about 24, but they were whistling like a terrible noise they made, that you-- you get scared before they hit the ground.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were-- we were already encountering these missiles coming into the city.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the same thing-- raus, raus.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Schnell.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "As they-- the SS were watching us, the Ukrainians, you could see Germans surrounding the locomotives, hanging onto everything they could hold onto, running.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They put us in the-- in cars.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "First they promised us they were going to take us to another factory.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But when we came to the other factory, there was one SS man and his name was Batenschlager.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He was standing at the front door and says, [GERMAN] to the train.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[GERMAN] to the-- straight to the train.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We came to the train.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They were crying as we're walking around.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They were afraid for the-- of Russians, you know, because they were countrymen.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They put us in there and we stayed until about 1:00 in the morning, loaded into the trains.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And about 1:00, the train took off for Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We came to Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "First of all, they picked up the police that were the real-- the real murderers, you know?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they disappeared.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You didn't see them anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there were so many people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were bringing in people from all over.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "From all the Polish camps, you know, and from Poland.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we-- they assigned us to the barrack 52.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And 12 people to a bunk.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If you wanted to turn around, everybody had to turn around.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And people were dying like flies.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
